name: Awesome Spool Up! Cargolux 747-4R7F [LX-UCV] Night Takeoff From Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everyone, in this video we have a Cargolux 747-400F departing Calgary International Airport, bound for Luxembourg. I also tried out a different spot, which has super close up views of aircraft and amazing spool-up sounds, as shown in the video. Listening to those RB211s roaring gives me goosebumps :) Hope you all enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
